The paper focuses on optimizing CNNs for inference, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of FPGAs for hardware implementation falls under the category of embedded systems (cs.ET) and system design and implementation (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the optimization of hardware utilization and energy efficiency, which could fall under the category of architecture (cs.AR).
